cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CV, cs.NE, cs.DC 

This paper discusses the comparison of open source frameworks for machine learning, which falls under the category of machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The use case of single threaded and multi threaded modes suggests that it may also fall under the category of computer vision (cs.CV) and neural networks (cs.NE). Additionally, the performance tests on the MNIST dataset may also suggest a category of distributed and parallel computing (cs.DC).
